                "abstract": "Summary: The HyPhypackage is designed to provide a flexible and unified platform for carrying out likelihood-based analyses on multiple alignments of molecular sequence data, with the emphasis on studies of rates and patterns of sequence evolution. © The Author 2004. Published by Oxford University Press. All rights reserved.",
